{"tid":2096300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"只會愈黎愈多post叫人唔好走","createTime":"2020-07-06T04:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T06:13:53.000Z","uid":81236,"like":53,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a8e6c4c2f87414b98d05e394377c0f4c54235d96","tid":2096300,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T04:48:03.000Z","msg":"但唔係同你講留低係香港等煲底<br />\n<br />\n亦都唔係話會留低比人告入左既人<br />\n<br />\n而係講：<br />\n<br />\n外國點會咁好手收留你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到外國無工做無收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外國經濟唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一去到無醫療無福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你自己諗清楚<br />\n<br />\n邊個有錢佬有權有勢既子女唔係係英美澳加？<br />\n<br />\n邊個有錢佬有權有勢既人無外國護照？<br />\n<br />\n中產死都要子女出國<br />\n<br />\n退休外國享受<br />\n<br />\n甚至洗過千萬投資移民<br />\n<br />\n點解？點解？點解？<br />\n<br />\n一定係因為外國經濟差，有錢佬去打救經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定係因為外國冇好人，有權有勢去教導人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定係外國冇工好做，過去創造就業機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定係外國福利差環境差，成就大義去呼吸有害空氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔抵得半賣半送香港人拎英國護照<br />\n<br />\n唔抵得香港人洗咁少錢就可以移民外國<br />\n<br />\n唔抵得可能比人政治審查去唔到但你去到<br />\n<br />\n唔抵得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2571fd4e3b38ce29f1bddcbf682f75c7d5485da0","tid":2096300,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T04:49:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f8e835fa438ec429a896f86fcf99d891698c93","tid":2096300,"u